%Y A309585 Cf. A214028.
%Y A309585 For a list of sequences related to the numbers of zeros in a fundamental period of {x(n)}, where {x(n)} is a sequence defined by x(0) = 0, x(1) = 1, x(n+2) = m*x(n+1) + x(n), see A053032.
